Recipe
A valid recipe consists of:
    a title
    optional: a short description
    optional: 1..n tags
    optional: 1..n yields
    the ingredients as 1..n ingredient groups
    optional: instructions

- recipe
    - id field
    - title field:string ("guacamole")
    - description field:string ("Some people call it guac")
    - tag field{:array, string} (["sauce", "vegan"])
    - yields field{:array, string} (["4 Servings", "200g"])
    - ingredients field{:map, string} ({amount: "1", item: "avocado"})
    - instructions field:string ("Remove flesh from avocado and roughly mash with fork. Season to taste with salt pepper and lemon juice.")

